OL,4,Cgrandmother by careless driving avoids
OL,5,Cjail
OL,7,FA nurse convicted of causing the death
OL,8,Fof a grandmother in a head-on smash as
OL,9,Fshe returned home from working a 12-
OL,10,Fand-a-half-hour night shift has
OL,11,Favoided a custodial sentence.
OL,13,FForty-eight-year-old Angela Hislop's
OL,14,Fred Mercedes GLE 300 crossed into the
OL,15,Fopposite carriageway and struck a grey
OL,16,FKia Venga vehicle driven by 72-year-
OL,17,Fold Janette Davidson from Kelso who
OL,18,Fdied from her injuries.
