OL,5,Cjail
OL,7,FThe crash happened close to Floors
OL,8,FCastle, Kelso, Roxburghshire, on 11
OL,9,FNovember 2022.
OL,11,FHislop was found guilty by a jury of
OL,12,Fcausing death by careless driving
OL,13,Ffollowing a three-day jury trial at
OL,14,FJedburgh Sheriff Court last month.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/11
