OL,4,Cgrandmother by careless driving avoids
OL,5,Cjail
OL,7,FHislop ` who had been working her long
OL,8,Fnight shift at the accident and
OL,9,Femergency department at Borders
OL,10,FGeneral Hospital near Melrose,
OL,11,FRoxburghshire - denied feeling tired
OL,12,Fin the lead-up to the crash, telling
OL,13,Fthe court she believed she was fine to
OL,14,Fdrive.
OL,16,FBut passing sentence at Selkirk
OL,17,FSheriff Court, Sheriff Peter Paterson
OL,18,Fsuspected there was an element of
OL,19,Ffatigue involved which would have been
OL,20,Fan aggravating factor for the offence.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/11
