OL,4,Cgrandmother by careless driving avoids
OL,5,Cjail
OL,7,FHe said: "I strongly suspect that you
OL,8,Fknew you were tired but in some
OL,9,Fmeasure that is speculation."
OL,11,FHislop now works 7.30am to 5.30pm
OL,12,FMonday to Friday and gets a lift to
OL,13,Fand from work by colleagues.
OL,15,FAs a result, Sheriff Paterson imposed
OL,16,Fa 12-month night curfew at her home in
OL,17,FKelso between the hours of 7pm and
OL,18,F6.30am which will be electronically
OL,19,Fmonitored and she was banned from
OL,20,Fdriving for 12 months.
