OL,5,Cjail
OL,7,FThe sheriff said: "This is clearly a
OL,8,Ftragedy primarily for the victim's
OL,9,Ffamily ` her husband and daughters `
OL,10,Fand something they will never get over.
OL,12,F"There is nothing this court can do or
OL,13,Fsay that will achieve any form of
OL,14,Fcomfort or restoration and I accept
OL,15,Fthat you (Hislop) know that.
OL,17,F"It would be open to the court to
OL,18,Fimpose a custodial sentence but I am
OL,19,Fnot going to do that and there is a
OL,20,Fgenuine alternative to that."
