OL,5,Cjail
OL,7,F"While we know that no sentence will
OL,8,Fever bring Janette back we feel
OL,9,Ftoday's outcome is far too lenient and
OL,10,Fdoes not reflect our pain, the value
OL,11,Fof Janette or serve a lesson to others.
OL,13,F"Our priority now is to move forwards
OL,14,Fin relative peace as we look to the
OL,15,Ffuture and try to continue to live
OL,16,Fwith the same positivity and values
OL,17,Fshe lived by.
