OL,7,F"We'd like to thank everyone who has
OL,8,Fhelped and supported us over the last
OL,9,Ftwo years ` friends, family and beyond
OL,10,F` and we now ask that our privacy is
OL,11,Frespected as we move forwards."
OL,13,FDuring the jury trial, Hislop ` who
OL,14,Fsuffered serious injuries gave
OL,15,Fevidence ` gave evidence in which she
OL,16,Fdenied she was unfit to drive through
OL,17,Ftiredness.
