OL,7,FShe said: "I just remember a car being
OL,8,Fin front of me. I remember seeing a VW
OL,9,Fbadge and then swerving, and then a
OL,10,Fbang."
OL,12,FBut she added: "I don't know if there
OL,13,Fwas another car."
OL,15,FJohn Adams, prosecuting, asked Hislop:
OL,16,F"When you got into your car, how did
OL,17,Fyou feel?"
OL,19,FShe replied: "Fine... excited because
OL,20,FI was on annual leave."
