OL,7,FEarlier defence lawyer Gary Miller,
OL,8,Fsaid: "It may be suggested you may
OL,9,Fhave been tired - were you tired?"
OL,11,F"No," she replied, "absolutely not."
OL,13,FWhen asked why her front window was
OL,14,Fhalfway down, Mrs Hislop added: "I
OL,15,Falways drive with the window down,
OL,16,Fthat's a habit I have; I'm menopausal,
OL,17,FI take hot flushes, it's unpleasant."
